      "title": "Laugfs slashes domestic LP gas prices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Laugfs Gas PLC has decided to reduce the prices of its domestic gas cylinders with effect from midnight today (Aug 17).",
        "Accordingly, the price of a 12.5 kg cylinder has been slashed by Rs. 1,050."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
